Key Match Events: Albert Gronbaek and Yussuf Poulsen scored apiece to hand Denmark a vital win in their UEFA Nations League clash
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Eagles were underwhelming here, failing to bring their A-game to the fore, and spending much of the clash on the backfoot
Others: Kasper Schmeichel saved both shots he faced and came away with a clean sheet too
Pierre-Emile Hojbjerg completed passes in triple digits (100)
